The paper deals with dynamic spectrum management in multi-user multi-carrier communication systems, which involves optimization and control of wireless networks. This falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
